 not only among the Normans. In the later Middle Ages it was overtaken by   John  , but continued to run second to that name until the 20th century, when the picture became more fragmented."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Baron William Ramsay was born in 1193, in Edinburgh, Midlothian, Scotland. He had at least 1 son. He died in 1255, at the age of 62."},"et":{"1193–1255":"1193–1255","1232–Male":"1232–Surnud","1255":"1255","1232":"1232","1193":"1193","Edinburgh, Midlothian, Scotland":"Edinburgh, Midlothian, Scotland"},"fi":{"1193–1255":"1193–1255","1232–Male":"1232–Kuollut","1255":"1255","1232":"1232","1193":"1193","Edinburgh, Midlothian, Scotland":"Edinburgh, Midlothian, Scotland"},"fr":{"1193–1255":"1193–1255","1232–Male":"1232–Décédé","1255":"1255","1232":"1232","1193":"1193","Edinburgh, Midlothian, Scotland":"Edinburgh, Midlothian, Écosse","lifeSummary":"Baron William Ramsay est né en 1193, à Edinburgh, Midlothian, Écosse. Il a eu au moins 1 fils. Il est décédé en 1255, à l’âge de 62 ans."},"de":{"1193–1255":"1193–1255","1232–Male":"1232–Verstorben","1255":"1255","1232":"1232","1193":"1193","Edinburgh, Midlothian, Scotland":"Edinburgh, Midlothian, Scotland","lifeSummary":"Baron William Ramsay wurde 1193 in Edinburgh, Midlothian, Scotland geboren. Er hatte mindestens 1 Sohn. Er starb 1255 im Alter von 62 Jahren."},"ht":{"1193–1255":"1193–1255","1232–Male":"1232–Desede","1255":"1255","1232":"1232","1193":"1193","Edinburgh, Midlothian, Scotland":"Edinburgh, Midlothian, Scotland"},"hu":{"1193–1255":"1193–1255","1232–Male":"1232–elhunyt","1255":"1255","1232":"1232","1193":"1193","Edinburgh, Midlothian, Scotland":"Edinburgh, Midlothian, Scotland"},"id":{"1193–1255":"1193–1255","1232–Male":"1232–Telah Meninggal","1255":"1255","1232":"1232","1193":"1193","Edinburgh, Midlothian, Scotland":"Edinburgh, Midlothian, Scotland"},"it":{"1193–1255":"1193–1255","1232–Male":"1232–Deceduto","1255":"1255","1232":"1232","1193":"1193","Edinburgh, Midlothian, Scotland":"Edinburgh, Mid